ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
PrecisReappointment of CORALIE BUTTIGIEG of Aurora, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five months or a period expiring on the day prior to the coming into force of the Balanced Refugee Reform Act, whichever period ends earlier, effective February 16, 2012.
